projectDetail: DailyTalk is a project aimed at facilitating daily communication and interaction among users through a web-based platform. Whether it's for team collaboration, informal discussions, or sharing updates, DailyTalk provides a convenient space for users to engage in conversation share multimedia content and stay connected.
